create input.css file and paste it
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
****************************************
in terminal put the belove code
npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./src/output.css --watch
 it will create css folder and its inside main.css also.
**************************************************************
afterthat put the belove lines in package.json 
"scripts": {
    "build": "tailwindcss -i ./input.css -o ./css/main.css",
    "watch": "tailwindcss -i ./input.css -o ./css/main.css --watch"
  }

  later in terminal npm run build
  after npm run watch
