then create index.html
1.mx-auto - margin right to left  x axis
2.my- auto - margin top to bottom y axis
3.mt - margin top
4.mb - margin bottom 
5.mr,ml - margin right,and left
.flex.px-3.pt-3.justify-between means <div class="flex px-3 pt-3 justify-between"></div>
6.a.pt-1 means anchor tag <a href="" class="pt-1"></a>
7.section#hero means <section id="hero"></section>




